---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CTAButton from '../components/CTAButton.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Building secure, automated solutions in Azure"
  description="I’m Joey Pompeo, a .NET developer focused on clean code, automation, and helping teams ship faster with confidence."
  eyebrow="About Joey"
>
  <div class="space-y-8 text-text-light/80">
    <section class="space-y-4">
      <p>
        I’m Joey Pompeo, a .NET developer focused on building secure, automated solutions in Azure. I’ve spent the last
        few years designing APIs, serverless apps, and DevOps pipelines that make development smoother and deployments
        safer.
      </p>
      <p>
        I’m passionate about clean code, test-driven development, and helping teams work smarter with automation. From
        IaC modules to CI/CD guardrails, I look for ways to turn tribal knowledge into reliable systems.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Certifications</h2>
      <ul class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
        <li class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-surface-dark/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-light/80">
          AZ-104 — Microsoft Certified Azure Administrator Associate
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-surface-dark/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-light/80">
          AZ-204 — Developing Solutions for Microsoft Azure
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-surface-dark/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-light/80">
          AZ-400 — Designing and Implementing Microsoft DevOps Solutions
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Résumé</h2>
      <CTAButton href="/assets/Joey-Pompeo-Resume.pdf" download variant="secondary">
        Download Résumé (PDF)
      </CTAButton>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
